{
  "texts": [
    "Due to the synergy between its different components, the model has been assured of being not just highly accurate but also interpretable.",
    "This makes it a truly robust solution for colorectal cancer detection and segmentation.",
    "By the fact that this model is built on carefully considered tradeoffs between complexity and accuracy, it will turn into a practical and deployable option within the medical diagnostic domain.",
    "The proposed PolynetDWTCADx model has achieved superior performance in both detection and segmentation for colorectal cancer when compared to standalone models and other state-of-the-art methods.",
    "Thus, the proposed framework achieved 92.3% testing accuracy with a Dice Coefficient of 0.96 and an IoU of 0.93, which outperformed CNN standalone models and conventional U-Net-based segmentation methods."
  ]
}